race.description: Ray White Ipswich, Tempus Two Mdn Plate
race.comment: HARD AS BROK (4) stepped up to this trip at Eagle Farm and just missed. Cherry-ripe now and will find this a lot easier. Ben Thompson sticks aboard the Vandyke-trained galloper and he's sure to take beating. AVERRED (2) was beaten 3L in the same race and didn't have the best of it. Peaks and may get closer today. JEDIAH (3) has had plenty of chances but improved last time beaten 2.5L over 1625m at Toowoomba. Steps up a level this time, but in this line-up, he's capable of getting some of the prize money. JADATAN (6) was well supported at Toowoomba but didn't finish it off. Drops back in trip and may prove the best of the rest.
